products.title: Baltimore Linen (Moisture Resistant)
products.metadescription: Buy made to measure baltimore linen (moisture resistant) bathroom vertical blinds from soeasy blinds. Order quality bathroom vertical blinds online today at low prices with fast uk delivery
products.productdescription:
Min width: 250mm max width: 5000mm
 	min drop: 500mm max drop: 4000mm
 	fabric composition: 25% fibreglass/ 75% pvc
 	louvre width: 89mm &amp; 127mm
 	guarantee: 12 months
